APPLICATION_DESCRIPTION: This application and its databases provide shared functionality, data consumption, and reporting across Finance Technology as we migrate our systems to the cloud.Currently, various on-premise Finance systems maintain duplicate upstream data individually, and maintain separate code bases for similar functionalities that we intend to avoid in the cloud by building shared databases, APIs, and a Finance Reporting Portal,The initial target users are other Finance applications that will interface with this application/database as they migrate to the cloud, but the system will be directly accessible (via a Reporting/Portal) by Finance business users eventually once we have a number of Finance applications migrated to the cloud.This application does not store calculation rules, nor process/transform data; only facilitates unified data sharing and reporting.
